    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "You can do so by using css:\n\n``` css\nais-pagination--item__next, ais-pagination--item__prev {\n  display: none;\n}\n```\n\nWe only provide options for use cases where we think it will provide a good UX. What is the usecase where you would like to hide the prev/next links?\n",
